                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4442" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0631</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9184 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Y企业：舆论管理就是价值管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Y Enterprise: public opinion Management is value Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵青华，甘秋月，孟丽娜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Y企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共关系/外事部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">舆论；舆论危机；舆论管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Public opinion;Public opinion crisis;Public opinion management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">古语有言，“自古圣贤，乐闻诽谤之言，听舆人之论”，说明古人很早就认识到了倾听公民意见和言论的重要性。如今信息技术快速发展，互联网已成为舆论传播的主要平台，越来越多的人能够迅速、及时地对事件作出评论，多种观点堆砌下，民众很难抽丝剥茧、发现真相。因此对于企业来说，对网上的负面舆论进行及时有效应对是至关重要的，但Y企业显然未认识到这一点。本案例描述了2018年Y企业面临的一次舆论危机，围绕其不同阶段进行展开。剖析Y企业公关事务部石部长的心路历程不难发现，他从一开始的不以为意，到网民不买账的始料不及，再到年报发布股价暴跌时的意志消沉，最后在自曝其短后才大彻大悟，真正重视起舆论管理工作。不得不说这次舆论危机为Y企业的舆论管理敲响了警钟，相信Y企业以后在应对舆论危机时能更加游刃有余。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the old saying goes,&quot; the ancient sages, the words of slander, listening to the theory of people &quot;shows that the ancients had long recognized the importance of listening to the opinions and words of citizens. Nowadays, the rapid development of information technology, the Internet has become the main platform for public opinion dissemination, more and more people can quickly and timely comment on the event, a variety of views piled up, people are difficult to pull the cocoon and find the truth. Therefore, it is very important for enterprises to deal with the negative public opinion on the Internet in a timely and effective manner, but Y enterprises obviously do not realize this. This case describes a public opinion crisis facing Y companies in 2018, surrounding its different stages  Lines open. Analysis of the Y corporate public relations affairs minister Shi&#39;s mind course is not difficult to find, he from the beginning of the disapproval, to the Internet users did not buy the unexpected, and then to the annual report when the stock price plummeted, and finally in the self-disclosure of its short before the great understanding, really attention to public opinion management work. Had to say this public opinion crisis for Y enterprise&#39;s public opinion management sounded the alarm bell, believed that Y enterprise in the future in response to public opinion crisis can be more easily. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业价值管理》、《证券投资学》、《高级财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">舆论危机</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-03</td>
                            </tr>
